room_title: Escape room "Vacation Vandals" by Key Quest in Spokane
review: Our volleyball team played here during a big tournament. The service was great and the team had a blast. Dress light as it is hot as heck inside the arena. It would be great if they had a little bit bigger space to have a team lunch but it worked fine.
